adept.common - package adept.common
Provides common data structures for use in the ADEPT framework, including the input Document and its TokenStream containing every Token, and the output HltContentContainer containing multiple kinds of annotations, such as EntityMention and Relation, which are based on the Chunk class.
adept.data - package adept.data
Provides interfaces for accessing databases and knowledge-bases such as NELL and the Paraphrase Database (PPDB).
adept.io - package adept.io
Provides I/O classes that handle reading/write files in different formats, including LDC Gigaword Corpus, ERE, CoNLL, email and plain text.
adept.module - package adept.module
Provides interfaces and classes to support DEFT TA1 algorithm implementations in the ADEPT framework, primarily based on the AbstractModule class along with a set of Processor interfaces, which together support specific subclasses for analysis, extraction, tagging and other algorithms.
adept.restapi - package adept.restapi
Provides interfaces for accessing DEFT algorithms as RESTful services
adept.serialization - package adept.serialization
Provides interfaces and classes for ADEPT data (de)serialization in XML, JSON and Binary format
adept.utilities - package adept.utilities
Provides utility classes and functions for creating ADEPT Document objects, for tokenization, regression test, benchmark test, profiler, command-line application and file conversions.
